  m_Name: TutorialDialogStatement_01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _text: "Master, the ritual is complete! The phylactery\u2019s dark fire has summoned
    your soul back to this mortal plane, restored by the souls of the fallen consumed
    within its cursed flames. I am but a spirit, my life sacrificed to ensure your
    return. I shall guide you, my lord, as you reclaim your full power."
